# game/kite_jobgirl 1_riddle.rpy:23
translate schinese jobgirl_0_473133ba:

    # jobgirl "Hey there!"
    jobgirl "嗨!"

# game/kite_jobgirl 1_riddle.rpy:25
translate schinese jobgirl_0_d1f98185:

    # jobgirl "Looking for another quest? I noticed you come here often, you must be a busy adventurer!"
    jobgirl "在找新悬赏吗?我发现你常来这里,看来你是位忙碌的冒险家!"

# game/kite_jobgirl 1_riddle.rpy:27
translate schinese jobgirl_0_04c60041:

    # you "Err, not exactly. The quests are not really for me; I have a group of, hem, workers, sometimes I get a job request here for one of them."
    you "呃,不完全是。这些任务其实不是我来完成的;我有一群,嗯,属下,有时候我会在这里接给她们的工作。"

# game/kite_jobgirl 1_riddle.rpy:29
translate schinese jobgirl_0_903385a5:

    # jobgirl "Oh, really? I could have sworn you were the adventurous type of guy..."
    jobgirl "哦,真的吗?我原以为你是那种爱冒险的类型..."

# game/kite_jobgirl 1_riddle.rpy:31
translate schinese jobgirl_0_f3ebb966:

    # you "Well, I can assure you that my life is not lacking in adventures at all! *wink*"
    you "好吧,我可以向你保证,我的生活绝对不缺少冒险!*眨眼*"

# game/kite_jobgirl 1_riddle.rpy:35
translate schinese jobgirl_0_f656c3ff:

    # jobgirl "Ahah! Well, at least you have a sense of humor. So, which kind of job are you looking for your subordinates?"
    jobgirl "哈哈!至少你很幽默。那么,你的下属需要什么样的工作呢?"

# game/kite_jobgirl 1_riddle.rpy:37
translate schinese jobgirl_0_462d9ecb:

    # you "Sorry but... It's private business. We don't even know each other!"
    you "抱歉,但是...这是私事。我们还没熟到那个地步!"

# game/kite_jobgirl 1_riddle.rpy:39
translate schinese jobgirl_0_94a55192:

    # jobgirl "Oh sure, sorry I forgot to introduce myself... Call me Scarlet."
    jobgirl "当然,对不起,我忘记自我介绍了...叫我斯卡莱特吧。"

# game/kite_jobgirl 1_riddle.rpy:41
translate schinese jobgirl_0_779bd35e:

    # you "Scarlet?"
    you "斯卡莱特?"

# game/kite_jobgirl 1_riddle.rpy:45
translate schinese jobgirl_0_1babc5c1:

    # jobgirl "Yeah, it's my battle name. We adventurers must defend our true identities to prevent the evil we fight from harming our beloved ones..."
    jobgirl "是的,这是我的绰号。冒险者们必须掩藏真实身份,以免我们所对抗的邪恶势力伤害我们深爱的人..."

# game/kite_jobgirl 1_riddle.rpy:47
translate schinese jobgirl_0_e4fc0205:

    # jobgirl "And some girls not working on the 'adventuring' side like to use fake names too, lest their dad finds out..."
    jobgirl "一些不从事'冒险'工作的女孩也喜欢使用假名,以免被父母发现..."

# game/kite_jobgirl 1_riddle.rpy:49
translate schinese jobgirl_0_3ba6eaa2:

    # you "I'm sure they do."
    you "我想她们确实如此。"

# game/kite_jobgirl 1_riddle.rpy:51
translate schinese jobgirl_0_40026f0e:

    # you "Well, my name is [MC.name]. Scarlet, was it? Wait, how did you come up with such a nickname? Did you get it from a fairy tale?"
    you "我叫[MC.name]。斯卡莱特,对吗?等等,你是怎么想出这个绰号的?是从童话故事里得到的灵感吗?"

# game/kite_jobgirl 1_riddle.rpy:53
translate schinese jobgirl_0_ff7e51d1:

    # jobgirl "Hey!!!" with vpunch
    jobgirl "嘿!!!" with vpunch

# game/kite_jobgirl 1_riddle.rpy:55
translate schinese jobgirl_0_b6422fd5:

    # jobgirl "What's wrong with my nickname? My hair is red, so I chose 'Scarlet' as my personal battle name!"
    jobgirl "我的绰号有什么问题吗?我的头发是红色的,所以我选择了'斯卡莱特'作为我的绰号。"

# game/kite_jobgirl 1_riddle.rpy:57
translate schinese jobgirl_0_d7421ffd:

    # you "Oh. I was hoping it would come with a better story."
    you "哦。我本以为它背后有更深层次的原因。"

# game/kite_jobgirl 1_riddle.rpy:59
translate schinese jobgirl_0_b628954f:

    # jobgirl "Shut up! It's a cool name, and I like it."
    jobgirl "闭嘴!这是个很酷的名字,我很喜欢。"

# game/kite_jobgirl 1_riddle.rpy:61
translate schinese jobgirl_0_1fb93c9f:

    # you "Ok, ok, don't get mad! I won't bug you anymore about your name."
    you "好吧,好吧,我不会再提你名字的事了。"

# game/kite_jobgirl 1_riddle.rpy:63
translate schinese jobgirl_0_16ef8e77:

    # jobgirl "Good, and it would be even better if you promise to stop being rude in general."
    jobgirl "很好,如果你发誓不再这么无礼地对待女孩就更好不过了。"

# game/kite_jobgirl 1_riddle.rpy:65
translate schinese jobgirl_0_ff7f4ddb:

    # jobgirl "Do you always treat girls like that? I bet you're still single, aren't you?"
    jobgirl "你对女孩总是这样的态度吗?我猜你肯定是个单身狗,对吧?"

# game/kite_jobgirl 1_riddle.rpy:67
translate schinese jobgirl_0_e1475bd6:

    # you "Uhm, actually... Now that you mention it, I must admit I'm not into any romantic relationship. My job keeps me busy..."
    you "呃,实际上...既然你问到了,我不得不承认我确实还是单身。繁忙的工作让我无暇顾及儿女情长..."

# game/kite_jobgirl 1_riddle.rpy:69
translate schinese jobgirl_0_f8c0605f:

    # jobgirl "I see... I guess you chose your job over women, haven't you?"
    jobgirl "我明白了...看来你把工作放在异性关系之上,不是吗?"

# game/kite_jobgirl 1_riddle.rpy:71
translate schinese jobgirl_0_ec3ab746:

    # you "Well, I wouldn't say that... Women are the most important part of my trade. They need constant training and management..."
    you "我不会这么说...女人是我事业中最重要的部分。她们需要持续的培训和管理..."

# game/kite_jobgirl 1_riddle.rpy:73
translate schinese jobgirl_0_ea1e33c5:

    # you "A brothel doesn't run itself, you know?"
    you "一家青楼可不是那么容易运转的,你知道吗?"

# game/kite_jobgirl 1_riddle.rpy:77
translate schinese jobgirl_0_79ce8c7f:

    # jobgirl "A brothel? So you're a pimp, right?"
    jobgirl "青楼?所以你是个皮条客,对吗?"

# game/kite_jobgirl 1_riddle.rpy:79
translate schinese jobgirl_0_685847ec:

    # you "Well..."
    you "嗯..."

# game/kite_jobgirl 1_riddle.rpy:81
translate schinese jobgirl_0_1e288093:

    # jobgirl "Ahahah, that's why you cannot find a girl!"
    jobgirl "啊哈哈,难怪你找不到女朋友!"

# game/kite_jobgirl 1_riddle.rpy:83
translate schinese jobgirl_0_f064d8ee:

    # you "On the other hand, I do have an active sexual life, just to inform you. So many girls from which I can choose to bring in bed with me."
    you "不过,我确实有非常丰富的性生活,很多女孩都愿意和我上床。"

# game/kite_jobgirl 1_riddle.rpy:85
translate schinese jobgirl_0_2330ce08:

    # jobgirl "You may feel lucky, being surrounded by so many girls, but how many of them are special to you? Are there any girls you don't want to share with clients? Special ones?"
    jobgirl "你可能觉得自己很幸运,莺歌燕舞美色环绕,但其中有多少人对你来说是特别的?有没有你不愿意与其他人分享的特殊的女孩?"

# game/kite_jobgirl 1_riddle.rpy:91
translate schinese jobgirl_0_0da82351:

    # you "There is one, my first slave, Sill; I don't let anyone put their hands on her, she's mine only!"
    you "我身边的就是,我的第一个奴隶希露;我不允许任何人碰她,她只属于我!"

# game/kite_jobgirl 1_riddle.rpy:93
translate schinese jobgirl_0_1432a25b:

    # jobgirl "I see. So, even a pimp can have a heart after all. Interesting..."
    jobgirl "原来如此。没想到连皮条客也也会动情。有意思..."

# game/kite_jobgirl 1_riddle.rpy:99
translate schinese jobgirl_0_c0687085:

    # you "I deal with pretty girls on a daily basis, but you can guess how my job is a great obstacle for a true relationship."
    you "我每天都在与漂亮女孩打交道,但你可以想象,我的职业是阻止我建立情感关系的一道难关。"

# game/kite_jobgirl 1_riddle.rpy:100
translate schinese jobgirl_0_97687702:

    # you "Some people consider slavery and whoring immoral, others just don't want to have any sort of business with a guy like me. Furthermore, I think I haven't encountered the right girl for me yet."
    you "有些人认为奴役和卖淫是不道德的,还有些人根本不愿意与我这样的人打交道。此外,我想我还没有遇到命定之人。"

# game/kite_jobgirl 1_riddle.rpy:101
translate schinese jobgirl_0_a65971c8:

    # you "I'd like to have a girlfriend, I'm human after all..."
    you "谁不想有个女朋友,毕竟我也是个普通人啊..."

# game/kite_jobgirl 1_riddle.rpy:103
translate schinese jobgirl_0_96a62a68:

    # jobgirl "I see. Your feelings are sincere, I can see it. I hope you're going to find her very soon."
    jobgirl "看得出你的发言很真诚。希望你能尽快邂逅天命之女。"

# game/kite_jobgirl 1_riddle.rpy:108
translate schinese jobgirl_0_a0eb8b3d:

    # you "Now, what about you? Do you have a boyfriend?"
    you "那么,你呢?你有男朋友吗?"

# game/kite_jobgirl 1_riddle.rpy:110
translate schinese jobgirl_0_2d699523:

    # jobgirl "Me? Mmh, well, let's say that my job doesn't really make me an ideal homemaker."
    jobgirl "我?嗯,不得不说我的工作确实不适合做个理想的家庭主妇。"

# game/kite_jobgirl 1_riddle.rpy:112
translate schinese jobgirl_0_652f84f7:

    # "You both laugh. You feel more relaxed and spend some time chatting."
    "你们两个都笑了起来。你感到放松许多,和她又聊了一会儿。"

# game/kite_jobgirl 1_riddle.rpy:114
translate schinese jobgirl_0_3c253c15:

    # "You learn that Scarlet lives here in Zan, in a tiny house near the plaza. She spends a lot of time running short quests."
    "你了解到斯卡莱特住在Zan,就在广场附近的一座小房子里。她大部分时间都在接一些轻松的低级悬赏。"

# game/kite_jobgirl 1_riddle.rpy:116
translate schinese jobgirl_0_d87b5c63:

    # jobgirl "Small quests are easy and don't take much time, so I do a lot of them, having more fun and less risks than doing a single, difficult one. Plus, in this way I can help more people! Isn't it perfect?"
    jobgirl "低级悬赏很简单,不需要花太多时间,所以我接很多这样的悬赏,乐趣更多,也更安全,比做一次高级任务轻松多了。而且这样我也可以帮到更多人!不是很完美吗?"

# game/kite_jobgirl 1_riddle.rpy:118
translate schinese jobgirl_0_0b17a876:

    # you "I guess so. You don't seem bored at all, always smiling around."
    you "我明白了。看起来你是个乐天派,特别爱笑。"

# game/kite_jobgirl 1_riddle.rpy:120
translate schinese jobgirl_0_ab1bcec7:

    # "One hour passes by while your conversation with Scarlet goes on."
    "你和斯卡莱特聊了一个小时左右。"

# game/kite_jobgirl 1_riddle.rpy:122
translate schinese jobgirl_0_6e182e58:

    # you "Oh shit, I have to hurry! Sorry Scarlet, business calls. It's been cool to know you better, I hope we can meet and talk again."
    you "哦,糟糕,我得赶紧走了!对不起斯卡莱特,我还有急事要处理。认识你真的很高兴,以后有机会再聊。"

# game/kite_jobgirl 1_riddle.rpy:124
translate schinese jobgirl_0_f36beaf9:

    # jobgirl "Sure [MC.name], I enjoyed our time together too. You know where to find me *winks*. See ya!"
    jobgirl "[MC.name],我也很享受在一起的时光。你知道在哪能找到我 *眨眼*。再见!"

# game/kite_jobgirl 1_riddle.rpy:126
translate schinese jobgirl_0_2eecd061:

    # you "(I must admit it, that girl is impressive.)"
    you "(我不得不承认,那个女孩很厉害。)"

# game/kite_jobgirl 1_riddle.rpy:153
translate schinese jobgirl_1_69893b10:

    # "You reach the posting board plaza looking for some more quests for your girls, when you notice Scarlet sitting on a bench nearby."
    "你走到悬赏栏前,想看看有什么新的悬赏可以让你的女孩们完成,此时你注意到斯卡莱特正坐在附近的长椅上。"

# game/kite_jobgirl 1_riddle.rpy:154
translate schinese jobgirl_1_1df7e374:

    # "She's totally absorbed in reading what seems to be an old scroll. "
    "她全神贯注地盯着一张似乎是古老卷轴的东西。"

# game/kite_jobgirl 1_riddle.rpy:156
translate schinese jobgirl_1_9237eaae:

    # jobgirl "Hey, [MC.name], glad to see you around again! What brings you here today? Business as usual?"
    jobgirl "嗨,[MC.name],很高兴再次见到你!今天来这里有什么事吗?像平常一样的生意?"

# game/kite_jobgirl 1_riddle.rpy:158
translate schinese jobgirl_1_05794613:

    # you "Hi Scarlet. That's right, I've come to see if there's any good quest for my girls. And you? What's that scroll?"
    you "嗨斯卡莱特。你说的没错,我来这里看看有没有什么好的悬赏让我的女孩们完成。你呢?那个卷轴是什么?"

# game/kite_jobgirl 1_riddle.rpy:160
translate schinese jobgirl_1_0db0f635:

    # jobgirl "Ah, this. It's a request from a client, a scholar who was trying to decipher it. I found it a few days ago and sold it to the guy, then he asked me to find a way to translate it."
    jobgirl "啊,这个啊。这是一位客户的委托,一位学者想要翻译上面的文字。我前几天发现了这个卷轴,卖给了那位学者,然后他让我想办法翻译它。"

# game/kite_jobgirl 1_riddle.rpy:161
translate schinese jobgirl_1_2f046d16:

    # jobgirl "But I'm no scholar. I only managed to get a raw translation but it's not enough to understand its meaning!"
    jobgirl "可惜我不是学者。我只能做些简单的翻译,这些文字对我来说太难了!"

# game/kite_jobgirl 1_riddle.rpy:163
translate schinese jobgirl_1_8d815c4d:

    # you "A scroll, uh?"
    you "一份卷轴,嗯?"

# game/kite_jobgirl 1_riddle.rpy:165
translate schinese jobgirl_1_13344540:

    # jobgirl "Yeah, an ancient one. The more I try to figure out what's written on it, the more my head hurts!"
    jobgirl "是的,一份非常古老的卷轴。我越想弄清楚上面写的是什么,越头疼!"

# game/kite_jobgirl 1_riddle.rpy:166
translate schinese jobgirl_1_3c4f0a44:

    # jobgirl "It's very difficult. Would you mind giving a hand to a damsel in distress? *winks at you*"
    jobgirl "这太难了。你愿意帮帮这位可怜的女士吗? *朝你眨眨眼*"

# game/kite_jobgirl 1_riddle.rpy:168
translate schinese jobgirl_1_b8c9d0a3:

    # you "Yeah sure, whatever... Let me see what's distressing you, little damsel..."
    you "好吧,不管怎么说...让我看看是什么让这位女士困扰..."

# game/kite_jobgirl 1_riddle.rpy:172
translate schinese jobgirl_1_01f31afe:

    # jobgirl "*laughs* You're a funny guy, has anybody ever told you that?"
    jobgirl "*笑*你真是个有趣的家伙,有人跟你说过吗?"

# game/kite_jobgirl 1_riddle.rpy:178
translate schinese jobgirl_1_a11e0574:

    # "She hands the scroll to you. The paper seems very old, the text is written in an old form of Xeros's common language, something you can handle easily."
    "她把卷轴递给你。纸张看起来很陈旧,文字是用克赛罗斯通用语的一种古老形式书写的,翻译对你来说应该不成问题。"

# game/kite_jobgirl 1_riddle.rpy:180
translate schinese jobgirl_1_8eeca005:

    # you "Let's see... Mmmh... This could be that, so this word can mean... and this one, should mean..."
    you "让我看看...嗯...这可能是这个意思,所以这个词应该是...那个词应该是..."

# game/kite_jobgirl 1_riddle.rpy:182
translate schinese jobgirl_1_ef54aa95:

    # jobgirl "*anxious* Sooo, did you get any hints? A translation?"
    jobgirl "*焦虑*所以,你有什么头绪吗?翻译出来了吗?"

# game/kite_jobgirl 1_riddle.rpy:184
translate schinese jobgirl_1_08609b58:

    # you "This is... a riddle?!" with vpunch
    you "这是...一个谜题?!" with vpunch

# game/kite_jobgirl 1_riddle.rpy:194
translate schinese jobgirl_1_ff29c8e9:

    # jobgirl "A riddle, uh? Interesting. It makes sense, since I found it in the Alikr desert, under a statue of a strange monster."
    jobgirl "一个谜题,嗯?有意思。这说得通,因为我在阿里克沙漠的一座奇怪的怪物雕像下面找到了它。"

# game/kite_jobgirl 1_riddle.rpy:196
translate schinese jobgirl_1_88f710f4:

    # you "A winged lion with a human face?"
    you "一只长有翅膀的人面狮子?"

# game/kite_jobgirl 1_riddle.rpy:200
translate schinese jobgirl_1_e66271c6:

    # jobgirl "H-how did you know that?" with vpunch
    jobgirl "哇,你怎么知道的?" with vpunch

# game/kite_jobgirl 1_riddle.rpy:202
translate schinese jobgirl_1_158567a6:

    # you "I'm just lucky to know the legend of the Sphinx, an ancient monster who loved to trap travellers and dared them to solve her riddles. Those who fail her trial are devoured."
    you "我只是很幸运地知道狮身人面像的传说,这是一种古老的怪物,喜欢设下陷阱,让路人来解开她的谜题。那些无法解开谜题的人都会被它吞食。"

# game/kite_jobgirl 1_riddle.rpy:204
translate schinese jobgirl_1_41490c94:

    # jobgirl "Eew, I hope I won't ever meet one in my lifetime!"
    jobgirl "呃,我希望我这辈子都不会遇到这种东西!"

# game/kite_jobgirl 1_riddle.rpy:206
translate schinese jobgirl_1_39580919:

    # you "Don't worry, it's just a myth, nobody has ever found such a creature as far as I know."
    you "别担心,这只是个神话,据我所知,从未有人真的发现过这种生物。"

# game/kite_jobgirl 1_riddle.rpy:208
translate schinese jobgirl_1_b1e01e69:

    # jobgirl "Good to know. Soo, what's the riddle's solution?"
    jobgirl "知道了。那么,谜题的谜底是什么?"

# game/kite_jobgirl 1_riddle.rpy:210
translate schinese jobgirl_1_7224535e:

    # you "You want me to solve it too? What if I get the wrong answer? Will you devour me?"
    you "你也要我解开它吗?要是我答错了呢?你会把我吃掉吗?"

# game/kite_jobgirl 1_riddle.rpy:212
translate schinese jobgirl_1_6978a924:

    # jobgirl "Gross! I'm not a monster, you know?"
    jobgirl "真恶心!我可不是什么怪物。"

# game/kite_jobgirl 1_riddle.rpy:214
translate schinese jobgirl_1_082c1548:

    # you "Ahah, I know... I was teasing. You're just a cute, innocent girl..."
    you "哈哈,我知道...我只是在逗你。你只是个可爱天真的女孩..."

# game/kite_jobgirl 1_riddle.rpy:216
translate schinese jobgirl_1_28c61f6a:

    # jobgirl "*blushes* D-don't mock me now... idiot... Anyway, the scholar is generous, so I don't mind sharing the pay If you want."
    jobgirl "*脸红*别、别嘲笑我了...白痴...不过,这位学者很慷慨,要是你想,我可以与你分享报酬。"

# game/kite_jobgirl 1_riddle.rpy:218
translate schinese jobgirl_1_decc78d7:

    # you "Ok, let's see then..."
    you "好的,那就让我来看看吧..."

# game/kite_jobgirl 1_riddle.rpy:226
translate schinese jobgirl_1_39553eca:

    # you "This riddle is quite ancient, did you know that?"
    you "这个谜题有些年头了,你听说过吗?"

# game/kite_jobgirl 1_riddle.rpy:228
translate schinese jobgirl_1_c29f098d:

    # jobgirl "Really? I've never heard of it before. However, it explains why it's written in such a weird way..."
    jobgirl "真的?我以前从未听说过。不过,这也难怪这么晦涩难懂..."

# game/kite_jobgirl 1_riddle.rpy:230
translate schinese jobgirl_1_0a3c2819:

    # you "Good point. Now the solution is-"
    you "很好。那么谜底是-"

# game/kite_jobgirl 1_riddle.rpy:232
translate schinese jobgirl_1_ee32c713:

    # jobgirl "Wait, are you giving me the answer without asking for a reward?"
    jobgirl "等等,你是说你不需要任何报酬就告诉我答案吗?"

# game/kite_jobgirl 1_riddle.rpy:234
translate schinese jobgirl_1_4818ec14:

    # you "A reward? Do people usually demand damsels in distress a reward for rescuing them?"
    you "报酬?人们通常都会要求困扰的女孩给予报酬作为回报吗?"

# game/kite_jobgirl 1_riddle.rpy:236
translate schinese jobgirl_1_5a80f950:

    # jobgirl "*smiles* Hihi, I guess they don't... Anyway, thank you very much!"
    jobgirl "*笑着*嘻嘻,看来他们好像不会这样做...总之,非常感谢你!"

# game/kite_jobgirl 1_riddle.rpy:238
translate schinese jobgirl_1_9339a2bb:

    # "The girl approaches your face and gives you a soft kiss on the cheek."
    "女孩靠近你的脸,粉唇轻轻点了一下。"

# game/kite_jobgirl 1_riddle.rpy:242
translate schinese jobgirl_1_e2023b8c:

    # jobgirl "This is just to let you know that damsels in distress appreciate their savior's help. *winks*"
    jobgirl "这只是为了让你知道,受困的公主会感激勇者的帮助。*眨眼*"

# game/kite_jobgirl 1_riddle.rpy:244
translate schinese jobgirl_1_258e89dc:

    # you "Ehrm, thank you, I guess... So, as I was saying, the solution is..."
    you "呃,谢谢,我想...那么,正如我之前说的,谜底是..."

# game/kite_jobgirl 1_riddle.rpy:248
translate schinese jobgirl_1_04efb9b0:

    # you "Aren't you forgetting something babe? Since this is a help request, there should also be a reward, am I right?"
    you "你是不是忘了什么,亲爱的?既然这是求助,那理应有相应的报酬,对吗?"

# game/kite_jobgirl 1_riddle.rpy:250
translate schinese jobgirl_1_a32f4012:

    # jobgirl "Wait, are you asking to be compensated for {i}this{/i}? Seriously?"
    jobgirl "等等,你是在要求报酬?为了{i}这个{/i}?认真的吗?"

# game/kite_jobgirl 1_riddle.rpy:252
translate schinese jobgirl_1_b43da79b:

    # you "Try to understand, I'm a businessman and this is just another job. If it was this easy, you would have done it yourself. How about a hundred coins?"
    you "请理解,我是个生意人,这只是另一项工作而已。如果这太简单,你自己就能解决了。一百枚金币怎么样?"

# game/kite_jobgirl 1_riddle.rpy:254
translate schinese jobgirl_1_1decdb77:

    # jobgirl "(*stares at you from head to feet*) Did they ever tell you that you're as cold as an iron bar? Are you sure you have a beating heart in your chest?"
    jobgirl "(*上下打量你*)没人告诉过你,你的心冷得像坨铁吗?你确定你的心脏还在跳动吗?"

# game/kite_jobgirl 1_riddle.rpy:256
translate schinese jobgirl_1_e122b685:

    # you "There's no need to say such things, you know? I'm not asking for the moon, just a small reward for a small task, that's all!"
    you "不至于不至于,你知道吗?我又不是要你去把星星摘下来,只是想要一点小小的回报,仅此而已!"

# game/kite_jobgirl 1_riddle.rpy:258
translate schinese jobgirl_1_9f5140a9:

    # jobgirl "Yeah, whatever. Fine. I'll pay you."
    jobgirl "好吧,随你怎么说。我会付钱的。"

# game/kite_jobgirl 1_riddle.rpy:260
translate schinese jobgirl_1_6cec30bc:

    # "She gives you a small bag of coins."
    "她给了你一小袋金币。"

# game/kite_jobgirl 1_riddle.rpy:268
translate schinese jobgirl_1_32438381:

    # jobgirl "Happy now?"
    jobgirl "现在满意了吗?"

# game/kite_jobgirl 1_riddle.rpy:270
translate schinese jobgirl_1_56b2cbc0:

    # you "Deal. So, here's the solution..."
    you "成交。那么,谜底是..."

# game/kite_jobgirl 1_riddle.rpy:274
translate schinese jobgirl_1_cb6f8254:

    # you "You really got it a few days ago and didn't get the solution yet?"
    you "你几天前就已经知道谜底了,却一直没有告诉我吗?"

# game/kite_jobgirl 1_riddle.rpy:278
translate schinese jobgirl_1_122907e2:

    # jobgirl "Hey, what are you blabbing about!!! I'm not stupid, you know?" with vpunch
    jobgirl "嘿,你在说什么呀!!!我又不是傻瓜,知道吗?" with vpunch

# game/kite_jobgirl 1_riddle.rpy:280
translate schinese jobgirl_1_97de1fba:

    # you "Don't get narky darling, didn't mean any offense, it is just... well, the riddle is quite simple, it's also quite old and famous, don't you know?"
    you "别生气,亲爱的,我并非有意冒犯,只是...嗯,这个谜题很简单,而且也很出名,你不知道吗?"

# game/kite_jobgirl 1_riddle.rpy:282
translate schinese jobgirl_1_7f5196db:

    # "She stares at you, giving you the impression she's a bit resentful, so you wield your best smile, hoping she'll calm down a little and forgive you."
    "她瞪着你,她有些不高兴的感觉,于是你绽放出最灿烂的笑容,希望她能够冷静下来,原谅你。"

# game/kite_jobgirl 1_riddle.rpy:284
translate schinese jobgirl_1_50345bb6:

    # jobgirl "Ok, ok, I'll let it slide this time, but don't be mean to me again or I'll make you pay..."
    jobgirl "好吧,好吧,这次我就不计较了,但别再阴阳怪气我了,否则我会让你付出代价的..."

# game/kite_jobgirl 1_riddle.rpy:286
translate schinese jobgirl_1_be4c75ed:

    # jobgirl "Now tell me what the answer is, or I'll never be able to sleep again!" with vpunch
    jobgirl "现在告诉我答案是什么,否则我怎么都睡不着!" with vpunch

# game/kite_jobgirl 1_riddle.rpy:288
translate schinese jobgirl_1_a898ce2d:

    # "Now that she mentions it you notice she looks tired and drowsy. She probably hasn't slept since getting the scroll, trying to solve the riddle!"
    "她提起这事,你才发现她看起来很疲惫、昏昏欲睡。她可能自从拿到卷轴以来都没有合眼,一直在试图解开谜题!"

# game/kite_jobgirl 1_riddle.rpy:290
translate schinese jobgirl_1_8c4f26bc:

    # you "Right, no more jokes, I promise. Now, let's see, the solution should be..."
    you "好的,不开玩笑了,我向你保证。现在,让我们看看,谜底应该是..."

# game/kite_jobgirl 1_riddle.rpy:302
translate schinese jobgirl_1_872b1a72:

    # "You don't want her to be mad at you, right? Try again!"
    "你不想让她生你气,对吗?再试一次!"

# game/kite_jobgirl 1_riddle.rpy:306
translate schinese jobgirl_1_fc3f2391:

    # "Don't you know it? Molise doesn't exist! Try again!"
    "你不知道吗?莫利塞根本不存在!再试一次!"

# game/kite_jobgirl 1_riddle.rpy:320
translate schinese jobgirl_1_81710e34:

    # you "Man."
    you "天哪。"

# game/kite_jobgirl 1_riddle.rpy:324
translate schinese jobgirl_1_142446ee:

    # jobgirl "Which one?" with vpunch
    jobgirl "哪一个?" with vpunch

# game/kite_jobgirl 1_riddle.rpy:326
translate schinese jobgirl_1_34be61d7:

    # you "Mankind in general, doofus..."
    you "总的来说,呆头呆脑的..."

# game/kite_jobgirl 1_riddle.rpy:328
translate schinese jobgirl_1_b05b0c24:

    # you "I can explain the solution if you want."
    you "如果你想的话,我可以解释下谜底。"

# game/kite_jobgirl 1_riddle.rpy:330
translate schinese jobgirl_1_dc695aec:

    # "She doesn't look very convinced."
    "她看起来不太相信。"

# game/kite_jobgirl 1_riddle.rpy:332
translate schinese jobgirl_1_31c7da47:

    # jobgirl "Nah... Not now, at least. I'll give it to the client to get my reward! *smiles happily*"
    jobgirl "不,至少现在不行。我会把它交给委托人,获得报酬!*高兴地微笑*"

# game/kite_jobgirl 1_riddle.rpy:334
translate schinese jobgirl_1_375a276f:

    # you "Alright then. So, how much will he pay you?"
    you "好吧。那么,他会付你多少钱?"

# game/kite_jobgirl 1_riddle.rpy:336
translate schinese jobgirl_1_c28ed55e:

    # jobgirl "The guy is very rich, he'll pay me a thousand coins for this job!"
    jobgirl "那个人非常富有,他会为这个工作付给我一千枚金币!"

# game/kite_jobgirl 1_riddle.rpy:338
translate schinese jobgirl_1_6009c969:

    # you "Wow, not bad!"
    you "哇,不错啊!"

# game/kite_jobgirl 1_riddle.rpy:342
translate schinese jobgirl_1_4ef84674:

    # jobgirl "I'm so relieved... Now I don't have to worry about my outgoings for a long time!"
    jobgirl "总算能缓口气了...接下来很长一段日子我都不必担心生计了!"

# game/kite_jobgirl 1_riddle.rpy:344
translate schinese jobgirl_1_0c68dd5f:

    # you "Congratulations. What will you do with all that money?"
    you "祝贺你。你打算用这笔钱做什么?"

# game/kite_jobgirl 1_riddle.rpy:346
translate schinese jobgirl_1_e3008a1d:

    # jobgirl "I definitely want to spend a small sum for fun! Gonna plan a trip to the beach as soon as possible. Ooh my, I need a new bikini, and a lot of exercises to get fit for it!"
    jobgirl "首先花一点小钱玩乐!我得尽快计划一次海滩之行。哦,我需要买一件新的比基尼,还要减肥才能穿上它!"

# game/kite_jobgirl 1_riddle.rpy:352
translate schinese jobgirl_1_ae55d497:

    # "Lost for a moment in her thoughts and plans, she suddenly sprints to take her leave, but..."
    "她陷入了思绪和计划中,突然迈步想要离开,但是..."

# game/kite_jobgirl 1_riddle.rpy:363
translate schinese jobgirl_1_f5bbb1db:

    # "She miscalculated the distance between you and her. She ends up falling right in your arms."
    "她误算了你们之间的距离。她最终摔进了你的怀抱。"

# game/kite_jobgirl 1_riddle.rpy:368
translate schinese jobgirl_1_959d16f5:

    # "You almost fall back but manage to stand; she's light but quite energetic." with vpunch
    "你差点摔倒,但设法站稳了;她很轻,但充满了活力。" with vpunch

# game/kite_jobgirl 1_riddle.rpy:372
translate schinese jobgirl_1_2a22fab1:

    # jobgirl "Ooh, sorry, uhm... *blushes*"
    jobgirl "哦,抱歉,呃...*脸红*"

# game/kite_jobgirl 1_riddle.rpy:374
translate schinese jobgirl_1_67aed4eb:

    # "You look at her beautiful blue eyes, down to her pink lips and white skinned neck, until you stare at her cleavage. Can't avoid to look at her breasts since the feeling of them pushing on your chest is raising your heartbeat."
    "你看向她美丽的蓝色眼睛,到她粉红色的嫩唇和白皙的玉颈,最后盯着她胸前的峰谷。目光被她的双峰吸引,它们压在你胸前的感觉让你的心跳加速。"

# game/kite_jobgirl 1_riddle.rpy:380
translate schinese jobgirl_1_a014484f:

    # you "Holding you in my arms is the best thing I could ever hope for... I wish I could catch you again soon."
    you "佳人入怀是我最期盼的场景...我想就这么抱着你。"

# game/kite_jobgirl 1_riddle.rpy:382
translate schinese jobgirl_1_4542b940:

    # "The girl is so embarrassed that she can't help but stare down. She blushes so much that her face seems about to catch fire."
    "女孩沉默不语,只能低头。她得脸红得仿佛要着火了。"

# game/kite_jobgirl 1_riddle.rpy:386
translate schinese jobgirl_1_d068f1b1:

    # jobgirl "Thank you, gallant knight... You do know how to speak to a woman. My mom always said I was a catch, I guess you just proved it! *wink*"
    jobgirl "谢谢你,勇敢的骑士...你知道如何与异性交流。我妈妈一直说我很好搞定,我想她是对的!*眨眼*"

# game/kite_jobgirl 1_riddle.rpy:388
translate schinese jobgirl_1_c69937e7:

    # you "Don't mention it. And please let me know if you need my help again, it will be my pleasure to come to the rescue again."
    you "不客气。如果你需要我的帮助,请随时告诉我,我很高兴能再来帮你。"

# game/kite_jobgirl 1_riddle.rpy:397
translate schinese jobgirl_1_4d7929c8:

    # you "I see... I think you're ready for the bikini test right now! I know very few girls more fit than you... And even less girls with such a good figure!"
    you "我明白...我认为你现在已经做好试穿比基尼的准备了!没有几个女孩比你更合适穿比基尼...更别说像你一样身材火爆!"

# game/kite_jobgirl 1_riddle.rpy:399
translate schinese jobgirl_1_8a04707c:

    # "She leaves your arms and steps back a little."
    "她挣脱了你的怀抱,退后了几步。"

# game/kite_jobgirl 1_riddle.rpy:406
translate schinese jobgirl_1_db682ddc:

    # jobgirl "Really? Do you think I'm in good shape?"
    jobgirl "真的吗?你认为我的身材很好吗?"

# game/kite_jobgirl 1_riddle.rpy:408
translate schinese jobgirl_1_9432b3ca:

    # you "I dare say fantastic shape. You can definitely wear any bikini, with such eyes no man will be able to keep his stare away from you!"
    you "我敢说,你的身材简直是完美。你穿任何比基尼都绝对合身,是个有眼睛的男人都会忍住不盯着你看!"

# game/kite_jobgirl 1_riddle.rpy:410
translate schinese jobgirl_1_f0fca549:

    # "At your words she looks at her cleavage and naively pulls her top down a little."
    "听到你的话,她低头看了看自己的乳沟,天真地把上领往下拉了拉。"

# game/kite_jobgirl 1_riddle.rpy:416
translate schinese jobgirl_1_02829207:

    # jobgirl "What, these?"
    jobgirl "是,这样吗?"

# game/kite_jobgirl 1_riddle.rpy:420
translate schinese jobgirl_1_53973358:

    # you "Wow!" with vpunch
    you "哇!" with vpunch

# game/kite_jobgirl 1_riddle.rpy:422
translate schinese jobgirl_1_b91e6759:

    # jobgirl "Are they really as beautiful as you are sayin-"
    jobgirl "它们真的像你说的那么漂亮吗-"

# game/kite_jobgirl 1_riddle.rpy:423
translate schinese jobgirl_1_f53be934:

    # jobgirl "EH! Don't stare!" with vpunch
    jobgirl "诶! 别盯着看!" with vpunch

# game/kite_jobgirl 1_riddle.rpy:429
translate schinese jobgirl_1_7ff6596b:

    # you "I don't want to be rude, but... I really enjoyed the view!"
    you "我不想无礼,但是...我真的很享受这幅美景!"

# game/kite_jobgirl 1_riddle.rpy:433
translate schinese jobgirl_1_13183125:

    # jobgirl "Yeah, I'm sure you did. You'd better cherish that memory, because there won't be another one!"
    jobgirl "是啊,我相信你确实很享受。你最好珍惜这个记忆,因为再也不会有下次了!"

# game/kite_jobgirl 1_riddle.rpy:435
translate schinese jobgirl_1_be443405:

    # you "Oh, don't be shy, we both know you liked it, admit it..."
    you "噢,别害羞,我们都知道你喜欢它的,承认吧..."

# game/kite_jobgirl 1_riddle.rpy:437
translate schinese jobgirl_1_2ffedf70:

    # "She blushes a little."
    "她略微脸红了一下。"

# game/kite_jobgirl 1_riddle.rpy:439
translate schinese jobgirl_1_9483edbf:

    # jobgirl "N-no way!..."
    jobgirl "不-不可能!..."

# game/kite_jobgirl 1_riddle.rpy:443
translate schinese jobgirl_1_dc9ba118:

    # you "Anyway, feel free to ask for my help again, anytime."
    you "无论如何,随时欢迎你寻求我的帮助。"

# game/kite_jobgirl 1_riddle.rpy:447
translate schinese jobgirl_1_47405369:

    # "Without saying a word, you look at her while gently holding her close to you."
    "一语不发,你轻轻地把她拥入怀中。"

# game/kite_jobgirl 1_riddle.rpy:449
translate schinese jobgirl_1_0e5ec6f6:

    # "After a long moment she timidly steps away, a little embarrassed."
    "过了很久,她才害羞地远推开了你。"

# game/kite_jobgirl 1_riddle.rpy:456
translate schinese jobgirl_1_9bb41fd5:

    # jobgirl "You've saved me a second time today. You're very useful, you know?"
    jobgirl "这是你第二次救了我。你真是非常靠谱啊。"

# game/kite_jobgirl 1_riddle.rpy:458
translate schinese jobgirl_1_b109b706:

    # you "I just like to be helpful, that's all."
    you "我只是想做好事,仅此而已。"

# game/kite_jobgirl 1_riddle.rpy:460
translate schinese jobgirl_1_53995d81:

    # jobgirl "You say so, but in this city, most people think helping someone else is a waste of time. Especially those in your field. You are quite the whitefly. *smile*"
    jobgirl "虽然你这么说,但在这个城市里,大多数人认为帮助别人是在浪费时间。尤其是在你这个圈子里的人。你可真是一个奇怪的人。*微笑*"

# game/kite_jobgirl 1_riddle.rpy:462
translate schinese jobgirl_1_f802f622:

    # "You look at each other for a long moment."
    "你们静静对视了很长一段时间。"

# game/kite_jobgirl 1_riddle.rpy:467
translate schinese jobgirl_1_c3740cf6:

    # you "I have to go now, my business needs my attention. Come and see me anytime, if you want. You'll be welcome."
    you "我现在必须走了,我还有急事要处理。如果你想我的话,随时来找我。我随时欢迎。"

# game/kite_jobgirl 1_riddle.rpy:469
translate schinese jobgirl_1_f30c4b0a:

    # jobgirl "Thank you, really! If it wasn't for you, I'd still be on that stupid riddle! See ya!"
    jobgirl "非常感谢!要不是你,我还在纠结那个愚蠢的谜题呢!再见!"

# game/kite_jobgirl 1_riddle.rpy:471
translate schinese jobgirl_1_b8a24d3f:

    # you "Bye!"
    you "再见!"

